  "detailed_description": "<h1>Reviews</h1><p><i>\"I was really impressed with this game, despite the art being simple, it is very beautiful and fits very well with the game, I really enjoyed the challenge of some stages, trying to pass it all without taking damage is very fun.\"</i><br> Steam Reviewer<br><br><i>\"A simple but very beautiful pixel art and a very well done level design.\"</i><br> Steam Reviewer</p><br><h1>About the Game</h1>This is a retro-style 2D platformer with suspenseful elements. You must find the way out of this cave without getting caught by the monsters and traps that appear unexpectedly with each new level.<br><br><strong>Main objective</strong> is to share a little about the sensations experienced by a person suffering from panic and anxiety disorders as a form of <strong>empathy and awareness</strong> (based on my personal experience).<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Easy to control</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2106770/extras/84e511270d83124a30f989a51e668260.poster.avif?t=1662557233\" width=600 height=262 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2106770/extras/84e511270d83124a30f989a51e668260.webm?t=1662557233\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2106770/extras/84e511270d83124a30f989a51e668260.mp4?t=1662557233\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >It's better to look around!</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2106770/extras/113ddefa336f04222a1b0ea2b0bf2dad.poster.avif?t=1662557233\" width=600 height=262 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2106770/extras/113ddefa336f04222a1b0ea2b0bf2dad.webm?t=1662557233\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2106770/extras/113ddefa336f04222a1b0ea2b0bf2dad.mp4?t=1662557233\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Agility and precision</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2106770/extras/103e5c8cfc51d110248f2d16086bcade.poster.avif?t=1662557233\" width=600 height=262 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2106770/extras/103e5c8cfc51d110248f2d16086bcade.webm?t=1662557233\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2106770/extras/103e5c8cfc51d110248f2d16086bcade.mp4?t=1662557233\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Checkpoint System</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2106770/extras/38ae5b4f0070178b2a1731e7b80f3990.poster.avif?t=1662557233\" width=600 height=262 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2106770/extras/38ae5b4f0070178b2a1731e7b80f3990.webm?t=1662557233\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2106770/extras/38ae5b4f0070178b2a1731e7b80f3990.mp4?t=1662557233\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> There are <strong>20 levels</strong> with different enemy and trap combinations<br></li><li> Each level has a timer to record your best times<br></li><li> Torches are used as checkpoints to help you out<br></li><li> <strong>Special effects</strong> of lights and cameras<br></li><li> Alternate controls (using WASD or Arrows)<br></li><li> Two types of jumps: <strong>normal and double</strong><br></li><li> Various enemies with different moves<br></li><li> Beware what comes from the darkness, there are <strong>hidden traps</strong>!</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "This is a retro-style 2D platformer with suspenseful elements. You must find the way out of this cave without getting caught by the monsters and traps that appear unexpectedly with each new level.<br><br><strong>Main objective</strong> is to share a little about the sensations experienced by a person suffering from panic and anxiety disorders as a form of <strong>empathy and awareness</strong> (based on my personal experience).<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Easy to control</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2106770/extras/84e511270d83124a30f989a51e668260.poster.avif?t=1662557233\" width=600 height=262 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2106770/extras/84e511270d83124a30f989a51e668260.webm?t=1662557233\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2106770/extras/84e511270d83124a30f989a51e668260.mp4?t=1662557233\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >It's better to look around!</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2106770/extras/113ddefa336f04222a1b0ea2b0bf2dad.poster.avif?t=1662557233\" width=600 height=262 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2106770/extras/113ddefa336f04222a1b0ea2b0bf2dad.webm?t=1662557233\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2106770/extras/113ddefa336f04222a1b0ea2b0bf2dad.mp4?t=1662557233\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Agility and precision</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2106770